      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a dependable choice for its next owner. The exterior retains a lovely finish with only minor surface scratches and one small chip on the rear bumper. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster and the floor mats. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly; it has a full service history, and the tires still have plenty of tread remaining. While not showroom perfect, it is a solid, reliable vehicle that requires no immediate investment.",
