    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This naturally aspirated mill utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The chassis remains taut with upgraded bushings and a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate common fatigue points. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain and suspension geometry remain dialed for precision turn-in and cornering stability. A turn-key enthusiast vehicle ready for the B-roads.",
      "price": 34500.0,
